{
  "stem": "3658.1",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And of course, I remember also that all the silver and the cutlery and the crockery and all the good things, we gave to our neighbors.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh yes, to look after, to put away.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And if there was some gold, they, they, they were hiding it, because they didn't-- they knew that we mustn't take anything like that with us.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So all the linen was at our neighbor's place, to the, you know, non-Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We gave to look after it for us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So that's what everybody did.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Everybody in town passed on their belongings, all the good things, and the rest you left the house just standing the way it was.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, there was no receipts or anything.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And when I came home, actually-- well, I'll tell you about that after-- but they-- we knew, because we were all told if anybody that comes home, that so-and-so has got, you know, stuff for us.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We knew which neighbor had received the goods.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they, they, they were looking after it for us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, it's a long story.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I'll tell you about it, because I want to tell you when I came back in a little.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But as I said, the neighbors were very nice and very good.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we were friends with their children, with their families.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was nothing but the best of-- we used to go into their house visiting.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They came to our house visiting, you know?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So a very normal neighborly life.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, not that I can remember.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No, it was not an issue in that part of the world.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In fact, it was a very nice life.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I remember that people used to, for instance, on Sabbath-- you know, the religious people, they can't carry things.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
